subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Janel McCarville had 16 points before leaving with an injury and Essence Carson had 10 to lead the Liberty (18-12) to a 69-61 victory against the Chicago Sky in a W.N.B.A. game at Madison Square Garden.
